# Security Page Layout Rules

• Main Content Area
  - Uses a vertical ScrollView
  - Contains:
    - Seed Phrase Section
    - Backup Section
    - Restore Section
  - Scrolls smoothly on all screen sizes
  - Prevents cramped UI on smaller devices
  - Keeps critical content accessible

• Bottom “Danger Zone” Section
  - Remains fully static (not inside the ScrollView)
  - Always visible at the bottom of the screen
  - Never scrolls away or hides
  - Acts as the final safeguard / last opportunity feature
  - Reinforces seriousness and prevents accidental oversight

• Overall Behavior
  - Top sections scroll
  - Bottom danger section stays anchored
  - Clean minimal UI (light/dark based on Settings)
  - Small section labels in both XML and Kotlin
  - Auto‑apply UI mode immediately when changed in Settings
